&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;186&quot; data-end=&quot;214&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;190&quot; data-end=&quot;214&quot;&gt;About Catch Creation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;216&quot; data-end=&quot;582&quot;&gt;Catch Creation is a global eCommerce company built for the digital age. We create, grow, and manage online brands that inspire customers and deliver real value through exceptional products and experiences. Our team thrives in a fully remote environment, combining creativity, data-driven strategy, and innovation to build scalable eCommerce solutions that perform.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;584&quot; data-end=&quot;845&quot;&gt;From concept to conversion, we specialize in developing brands that stand out in competitive markets—driven by a passion for design, storytelling, and customer satisfaction. Every product we launch reflects our commitment to quality, authenticity, and growth.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;847&quot; data-end=&quot;1044&quot;&gt;At Catch Creation, we believe great ideas can come from anywhere—and our remote-first culture allows talented people from around the world to collaborate, innovate, and bring those ideas to life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;detail-oriented and proactive Amazon Assistant&lt;/strong&gt; to support our growing e-commerce operations. The primary focus of this role is &lt;strong&gt;Amazon account management&lt;/strong&gt;, but experience with other e-commerce platforms (e.g., Walmart, Shopify, etc.) is highly valued.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you do not yet have hands-on experience with all platforms listed, &lt;strong&gt;we are open to candidates who are eager, coachable, and willing to learn new e-commerce systems and tools&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and manage &lt;strong&gt;Amazon shipment plans&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run and optimize &lt;strong&gt;Amazon Deals and Coupons&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform &lt;strong&gt;inventory forecasting&lt;/strong&gt; and stock monitoring&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage &lt;strong&gt;Amazon Creator Connections&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with and optimize &lt;strong&gt;Amazon PPC campaigns&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Handle &lt;strong&gt;Walmart account management&lt;/strong&gt; (if applicable)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor and resolve &lt;strong&gt;Amazon account health issues&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and optimize &lt;strong&gt;Amazon product listings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open, track, and resolve &lt;strong&gt;Amazon Seller Central cases&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct &lt;strong&gt;A/B testing&lt;/strong&gt; for listings and creatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform &lt;strong&gt;flat file uploads&lt;/strong&gt; and bulk listing updates&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Skills &amp;amp; Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience as an &lt;strong&gt;Amazon Virtual Assistant&lt;/strong&gt; or E-commerce Assistant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of &lt;strong&gt;Amazon Seller Central&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shipment plans&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Listings and flat files&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deals, coupons, and promotions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PPC basics&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent attention to detail and organizational skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to follow SOPs and meet deadlines&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have (But Not Required)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

