&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remote (Philippines) / Full-Time&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a US-based e-commerce company operating at scale across direct-to-consumer, retail, and TV channels. Our brands include products in the pet and home categories. We&#39;re building institutional-grade finance operations to support continued growth and strategic initiatives over the next 12-18 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re hiring a Senior Accountant or Finance Manager to own day-to-day accounting operations. You&#39;ll report directly to the CEO and be responsible for keeping our books clean, payments on time, and financial data accurate. This is a hands-on execution role with room to grow into a broader finance leadership position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Payments &amp;amp; Disbursements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accounts payable and accounts receivable management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vendor payment scheduling, including preparing and executing wire transfers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Credit card payment management and payoff scheduling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payroll audit and processing (Chase to Wise transfers)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Influencer and contractor payment processing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manual refund processing (PayPal)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reconciliation &amp;amp; Reporting&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Purchase order reconciliation and balancing against invoices and inventory received&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Daily cash reconciliation across multiple bank accounts and payment processors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bank and credit card reconciliations (Chase, Amex, Stripe, PayPal)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ad spend reconciliation (Meta, TikTok, AppLovin, Google) against invoices and charged payments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Inventory stock report reconciliation (bi-weekly)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Amazon and marketplace sales journal entries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tax &amp;amp; Compliance&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales tax filing and compliance (US, UK, AU) via TaxJar&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sales tax registration for new nexus states&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating with external tax partners (SimplyVAT, Zonkeepers)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Audit support and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt

