&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Catch Creation &amp;amp; Muddy Mat&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Catch Creation is a global e-commerce company that creates, grows, and manages online brands. Our flagship brand, Muddy Mat, is a 9-figure revenue, bootstrapped, profitable DTC pet products company the #1 selling indoor mat for cleaning dog paws, loved by millions of pet owners across America.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We operate across TV, DTC e-commerce, Amazon, TikTok Shop, and expanding retail partnerships with Home Depot, Costco, and Walmart. Our portfolio also includes Cloud K9 (anti-anxiety dog beds) and Wizz (pet stain remover). We are remote-first, lean, and move fast.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a hands-on, entrepreneurial Fractional CTO to provide senior technology leadership during a critical growth phase. You will work directly with the Founder/CEO and leadership team to own our technology strategy, lead our engineering team, and ensure our platforms can scale with the business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is not a consulting role where you write recommendations and disappear. We need someone who will embed with the team, make decisions, and drive execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technology Strategy &amp;amp; Architecture&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and execute our overall technology roadmap and platform architecture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate and recommend technology solutions that support multi-channel e-commerce growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure scalability, security, and reliability across all tech systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent technology in leadership and strategic planning meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
