&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Share your portfolio showcasing digital design work&lt;/strong&gt; — bonus if it includes eCommerce or pet-related brands&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
