&lt;p&gt;• Coordinate product sample shipments, inventory availability, and promotional calendars with teams&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;• Hold team accountable to KPIs while maintaining a collaborative, growth-focused partnership&lt;/p&gt;
