able in Northbeam or a comparable MTA platform; clear understanding of the difference between platform-reported and attributed performance&lt;br&gt;• Strong instincts for advertorial funnels: what makes one work, what kills CTR from ad to page, what kills conversion from page to offer&lt;br&gt;• Disciplined testing methodology — you can articulate how you isolate variables, when you call a test, and what your kill criteria are&lt;br&gt;• Comfortable owning a channel build from scratch — this is a zero-to-one role&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nice to Have:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Experience launching native in additional ecosystems: Revcontent, MGID, Yahoo DSP&lt;br&gt;• Background in pet, home goods, or general

